  "title": "Asst Sales Manager/ Sales manager",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preparation of sales quotations, sales follow-up, sales reports, cold callings, customer visits.</li>\n  <li>Identify key customers and establish strong relationships with key personnel's.</li>\n  <li>Understand the requirement of each customer.</li>\n  <li>Understanding the specific vessel technical specification to provide a customized equipment package solution.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the service team where applicable to offer total solution to customer.</li>\n  <li>Act as the primary point of contact for the customer, ensuring good customer service &amp; support. Address any concerns or issues promptly.</li>\n  <li>Monitor market trends and be updated on industry news and regulations. Understand competitor activities and customer preferences.</li>\n  <li>Proactively engagement with customers to build strong relationships and understand their evolving needs.</li>\n  <li>Attend industry events, trade shows and conferences to network and generate leads.</li>\n  <li>Prepare the budget associated with proposals or contract tender.</li>\n  <li>Negotiate and close sales with customers for complete order processing.</li>\n  <li>Identify opportunities to upsell or cross sell across product range and make.</li>\n  <li>Monitor sales performance and analyse variances to meet target.</li>\n  <li>Participate in sales &amp; marketing activities.</li>\n  <li>Assist to resolve payment issue with customers when necessary.</li>\n</ul>",
